<asp:Content ID="Content1" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent" runat="Server">
    <br />
    <table width="90%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" valign="middle">
                <span class="LabelsHeader"><b>Real Time Wireless Credit Card Processing for PDA, PocketPC
                    and J2ME enabled devices</b></span>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td align="left" valign="middle">
                <span class="LabelsBody">Merchants equipped with a compatible wireless PDA and Infinite
                    Peripheral's printer with integrated Mag-Stripe Reader, can connect to the Authorize.Net
                    Payment Gateway to submit, authorize and complete wireless credit card and electronic
                    check transactions.</span>
                <p>
                    <span class="LabelsBody">MobileCharge is a software application that is compatible with
                        various Palm OS, PocketPC, and Java 2 Micro Edition (J2ME) data-enabled PDA (personal
                        digital assistant) devices, allowing you to process credit card sales from any location
                        with access to wireless service.</span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span class="LabelsBody">With MobileCharge, credit cards can be swiped, authorized, and
                        charged without a traditional credit card terminal or wired computer. In addition,
                        merchants can view Authorize.Net reports from a wireless PDA. This service works
                        in conjunction with an Authorize.Net payment gateway account using the merchant's
                        account and password.</span></p>
                <p>
                    <span class="LabelsHeader"><b>Hardware Requirements:</b></span>
                    <br />
                    <span class="LabelsBody">Wireless data capable cellular PDA (PalmOne Treo 600, 650 &amp;
                        Samsung i700 are currently supported devices. Will work with PalmOne Treo 700 and
                        Blackberry 7100T, 7230, 7250, 7280, 7290, 7510, 7520, 7700 in near future).</span>
                    <br />
                    <span class="LabelsBody">IPC PP-50MS or PP-55MS printer&nbsp;</span>
                <p>
                    <span class="LabelsHeader"><b>Software Requirements:</b></span>
                    <br />
                    <span class="LabelsBody">MobileCharge application - MobileCharge™ is compatible with various
                        Palm OS™, Pocket PC™, and Java™ 2 Micro Edition (J2ME) data-enabled PDA devices.</span>
                <p>
                    <span class="LabelsHeader"><b>Other Requirements:</b></span>
                    <br />
                    <span class="LabelsBody">Authorize.Net payments gateway account</span>
                    <br />
                    <span class="LabelsBody">Data subscription from your wireless cellular provider</span>
